; Regression test for issue #577: automated virtual postings with multiple commodities
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/577
;
; When a transaction has multiple commodities and a null posting (auto-balanced),
; finalize() creates additional balancing posts with ITEM_GENERATED | POST_CALCULATED.
; Automated transactions must match these balancing posts so that the virtual
; postings reflect all commodities, not just the first one.

; Original bug report scenario: single transaction, three commodities,
; auto-balanced Equity posting matched by automated transaction.

= /^Equity:/
 (Virtual Account)        1

2011/01/01 Opening Balances
 Account1                 100 USD
 Account2                 100 GBP
 Account3                 100 EUR
 Equity:Opening Balance

test bal
             100 USD  Account1
             100 GBP  Account2
             100 EUR  Account3
            -100 EUR
            -100 GBP
            -100 USD  Equity:Opening Balance
            -100 EUR
            -100 GBP
            -100 USD  Virtual Account
--------------------
            -100 EUR
            -100 GBP
            -100 USD
end test

test reg
11-Jan-01 Opening Balances      Account1                    100 USD      100 USD
                                Account2                    100 GBP      100 GBP
                                                                         100 USD
                                Account3                    100 EUR      100 EUR
                                                                         100 GBP
                                                                         100 USD
                                Equity:Opening Balance     -100 EUR      100 GBP
                                                                         100 USD
                                Equity:Opening Balance     -100 GBP      100 USD
                                Equity:Opening Balance     -100 USD            0
                                (Virtual Account)          -100 EUR     -100 EUR
                                (Virtual Account)          -100 GBP     -100 EUR
                                                                        -100 GBP
                                (Virtual Account)          -100 USD     -100 EUR
                                                                        -100 GBP
                                                                        -100 USD
end test
